application_type_full: Outline planning permission: Some matters reserved
description: Full permission for: Demolition of the existing retail store and petrol station and the erection of a replacement retail store (13,059msq)); childrens tutoring facility (298msq); lobby/circulation space (1,707msq); energy centre (779msq); flexible retail, community floorspace (787msq); office floorspace (1,860msq) and 645 residential units with ancillary gym arranged in seven blocks including towers of 19, 28 and 37 storeys; 363 retail and 148 residential parking spaces; 882 cycle spaces together with associated open space, childrens play space, landscaping and public realm improvements along Wandsworth Road and a new route from Wandsworth Road to New Covent Garden;  Outline permission for 105msq of flexible A1, A2, A3, A4, D1 floorspace and 92 dwellings within 2 blocks. Floorspace for use in association with the proposed Nine Elms Northern Line station or A1, A2, A3, A4, D1 use.
